2500|$|As {{the most}} visible Berlin Wall checkpoint, Checkpoint Charlie is {{frequently}} featured in spy movies and books. A famous cafe and viewing place for Allied officials, armed forces and visitors alike, [...] ("Eagle Café"), is situated right on the checkpoint. It was an excellent viewing point to look into East Berlin while having something <b>to</b> <b>eat</b> <b>and</b> <b>drink.</b>|$|E
